"italic_en","text":"forgotten, and neglected"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"left,"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the fire: and another reading is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muforiTuwna","text_ar":"مُفْرِطُونَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning [they are]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"exceeding the limits assigned to them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K:) and another is ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mufar~iTuwna","text_ar":"مُفَرِّطُونَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"falling short of their duty"},{"kind":"text","text":"] to themselves, in respect of sins. (TA.) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Filled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"full;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a pool of water left by a torrent. (S, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","Az","O","Fr","K"]},{"entry_id":"n33605","headword_ar":"مُفْرِطٌ","root":"frT","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Exceeding the due bounds,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"just limits; acting extravagantly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a man:"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excessive;"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to anything; as, for instance, tallness, and shortness. (TA.) It is said in a trad. of 'Alee, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA taraY AljaAhila A_al~aA muforiTFA A^awo mufar~iTFA","text_ar":"لَا تَرَى الجَاهِلَ اـَلَّا مُفْرِطًا اَوْ مُفَرِّطًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou wilt not see the ignorant otherwise than exceeding the due bounds in what he doth or falling short of what he ought therein."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muforaTN","text_ar":"مُفْرَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n33606","headword_ar":"مُفَرِّطٌ","root":"frT","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muforaTN","text_ar":"مُفْرَطٌ"},{"kind":"text","t